Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.redblacktree

Class RedBlackTreeNode

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.redblacktree.RedBlackTreeNode
public class RedBlackTreeNode extends Object

Title: RedBlackTreeNode

Description

Class for creating individual nodes in the RB tree. Note that there are parent, left, and right attributes which are used to set the structure of the tree.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
